@PoeEconomy.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5216

### Get economy overview
GET {{PoeEconomy.Api_HostAddress}}/api/economy
Accept: application/json

###

### Refresh sections from poe.ninja nav HTML
### Paste the nav HTML from browser DevTools (right-click the left sidebar → Copy → Copy outerHTML)
POST {{PoeEconomy.Api_HostAddress}}/api/sections/refresh
Content-Type: text/plain

<div class="p-6"><h3 data-variant="subdued">General</h3><ul><li><a href="/poe2/economy/runesofaldur/currency" title="Currency"><span>Currency</span></a></li></ul></div>

